{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"126876-a-girl-called-cheeku","title":"A Girl Called Cheeku","description":"It's just an ordinary day for Cheeku and her friends. But then something extraordinary happens. Will Cheeku save the day? A story that celebrates individuality and reminds us that each one of us is special. ","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Swagata Sen Pillai"],"illustrators":["Manasi Parikh"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/126876-a-girl-called-cheeku"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/723773/size3/59eacf74760a6366ea11b0ecbb11fde2.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/723773/size6/59eacf74760a6366ea11b0ecbb11fde2.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/152474/size6/e566480475bc213689a89df1bf450cc1.jpg","text":"2/9","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/152466/size6/357bcce106414d26e5f7b88552e65b98.jpg","text":"Cheeku is not too big\nOr too small.\nShe's not too short\nOr too tall.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/152468/size6/73271b3b6b3267c842295e06a862e2b0.jpg","text":"She doesn't talk a lot,\nOr play too long.\nBut Cheeku always speaks up\nWhen she sees something wrong.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/152498/size6/bb119d2145ea7d5a3086fd6f0ae8b26f.jpg","text":"Cheeku won't be found\nSwimming in a pond,\nOr climbing a tree.\nIf you go to a busy market,\nCheeku won't be there\nOn a spending spree.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/152470/size6/27c474a7cb96c6a1628511efc78485e8.jpg","text":"One day there was a storm,\nAnd off went the light.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/153118/size6/8944947d732baf860e69cccd85cbb8c6.jpg","text":"The darkness and shadows\nGave everyone a fright.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/152472/size6/4b9f39022b068937c2dbaab0eca24769.jpg","text":"Cheeku was brave,\nShe didn't bawl.\nShe quickly lit a lamp,\nAnd told stories to all.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/152473/size6/163b4dd371f9390f470f1653431725aa.jpg","text":"With song and dance and stories, hooray,\nCheeku drove the darkness away.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":8,"words":109}}